773
00:33:31,340 --> 00:33:32,660
and Bao is still in the hospital.

774
00:33:33,420 --> 00:33:34,580
If we alert them now,

775
00:33:35,100 --> 00:33:36,840
Dian Lao'er might use it
against us later.

776
00:33:36,940 --> 00:33:37,780
Here's the plan.

777
00:33:37,790 --> 00:33:38,940
Er'leng, Big Eye Chen and I

778
00:33:38,940 --> 00:33:39,900
