779
00:33:39,900 --> 00:33:40,840
Don't act impulsively.

780
00:33:41,220 --> 00:33:42,060
Okay, hurry up.

781
00:33:55,340 --> 00:33:56,740
The food's really good here.

782
00:34:30,180 --> 00:34:31,420
Pushing your luck, huh?

783
00:34:33,740 --> 00:34:34,820
We're debt collectors,

784
00:34:35,300 --> 00:34:36,380
not murderers.

785
00:34:54,640 --> 00:34:56,740
When you're full and satisfied,
you won't miss home.

786
00:34:56,740 --> 00:34:57,940
When the debt's cleared,

787
00:34:58,540 --> 00:35:00,040
we'll treat you to something better.

788
00:35:03,140 --> 00:35:03,980
Thank you.

789
