in that car accident?

796
00:35:33,340 --> 00:35:34,180
Right?

797
00:35:34,810 --> 00:35:36,560
That guy stabbed someone.

798
00:35:36,670 --> 00:35:38,460
How could he just hide here so openly?

799
00:35:39,060 --> 00:35:40,890
What should we do then?

800
00:35:50,040 --> 00:35:50,940
Chen,

801
00:35:51,060 --> 00:35:52,040
