822
00:36:53,120 --> 00:36:53,960
Fill it up.

823
00:36:54,030 --> 00:36:55,030
All in.

824
00:37:00,360 --> 00:37:01,300
Done. Come on.

825
00:37:12,740 --> 00:37:13,580
Three.

