00:37:13,820 --> 00:37:14,660
Pass.

827
00:37:15,820 --> 00:37:16,660
Pass.

828
00:37:21,670 --> 00:37:22,540
Three.

829
00:37:22,990 --> 00:37:24,360
- Can't take it.
- Can't take it.

830
00:37:28,250 --> 00:37:30,500
I have never seen
such a way of playing cards.

831
00:37:30,860 --> 00:37:32,580
Are you guys messing with me?

832
00:37:33,220 --> 00:37:34,100
Is it fun?

833
00:37:34,540 --> 00:37:36,340
Messing with you for what?

834
00:37:36,340 --> 00:37:37,860
We just can't take it.

835
00:37:38,050 --> 00:37:39,730
This isn't Fight the Landlord.

836
00:37:40,250 --> 00:37:41,420
This is fighting against me.

837
00:37:46,660 --> 00:37:48,460
Who threw trash onto my boat?

838
00:37:48,460 --> 00:37:49,300
Come out!

839
00:37:49,700 --> 00:37:50,850
- Come out!
- Come out!

840
00:37:50,860 --> 00:37:52,020
- Come out!
- Search!

841
00:37:52,100 --> 00:37:53,060
Come out!

842
00:37:55,020 --> 00:37:56,260
Search over there!

843
00:38:02,900 --> 00:38:04,500
- Come out!
- Come out!

844
00:38:04,540 --> 00:38:05,380
What are you doing?

845
00:38:06,020 --> 00:38:06,860
Come out!

846
00:38:06,870 --> 00:38:07,650
Sit here.

847
00:38:25,020 --> 00:38:26,620
